name: 4-hydroxyphenylpyruvate dioxygenase
classes: Acting on single donors with incorporation of molecular oxygen (oxygenases);

comment: The Pseudomonas enzyme contains one Fe3+ per mole of enzyme; the enzymes from other sources may contain essential iron or copper.
